text: Mass in F Minor is a 1968 album by American rock band The Electric Prunes. Mass in F Minor may also refer to: *Mass No. 3, or Mass in F Minor, WAB 28, by Anton Bruckner (first performed 1872) *Mass in F Minor by Josef Schnabel (1767–1831) *Two settings of Mass in F minor by George Whiting (1840–1923) *Mass in F minor, op. 22 (published 1846) by Bernhard Molique *Mass in F minor, op. 51 (1934), by Egon Wellesz
title: Mass in F Minor (disambiguation)
